#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.116"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.116:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.116:0.2"
msgid "11. Tikavagga"
msgstr "11. Triads"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.116:0.3"
msgid "116. Uddhaccasutta"
msgstr "116. Restlessness"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.116:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, dhammā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three things."

msgctxt "an6.116:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an6.116:1.3"
msgid "Uddhaccaṃ, asaṃvaro, pamādo."
msgstr "Restlessness, lack of restraint, and negligence."

msgctxt "an6.116:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhammā."
msgstr "These are the three things."

msgctxt "an6.116:1.5"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr "To give up these three things you should develop three things."

msgctxt "an6.116:1.6"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an6.116:1.7"
msgid ""
"Uddhaccassa pahānāya samatho bhāvetabbo, asaṃvarassa pahānāya saṃvaro "
"bhāvetabbo, pamādassa pahānāya appamādo bhāvetabbo."
msgstr ""
"You should develop serenity to give up restlessness, restraint to give up "
"lack of restraint, and diligence to give up negligence."

msgctxt "an6.116:1.8"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya ime tayo dhammā "
"bhāvetabbā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the three things you should develop to give up those three things.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.116:1.9"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.116:1.10"
msgid "Tikavaggo ekādasamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.116:2.1"
msgid "Rāgaduccaritavitakka,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.116:2.2"
msgid "Saññā dhātūti vuccati;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.116:2.3"
msgid "Assādaaratituṭṭhi,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.116:2.4"
msgid "Duve ca uddhaccena vaggoti."
msgstr ""
